      <p class="lead mb-4 front-dialogue fw-light">
          KodeWreck, the official Competitive Programming Society of KIIT, was founded in 2022 by two visionary students, Aniket Kundu (Master @ Codeforces) and Ayush Raj (Expert @ Codeforces). Driven by a passion for algorithms and problem-solving, they created KodeWreck to ignite a competitive programming culture on campus, providing a platform where like-minded students could collaborate, compete, and grow.</p>

